(1, 'Ramiz Cəlilov Vəli', 'The official consultant of the German company \"Bredent\" in Azerbaijan and the owner of the pilot laboratory of the \"Bredent\" company in Azerbaijan and the \"Beyaz Dish\" clinic.', 'A dentist, also known as a dental surgeon, The dentist\'s supporting team aids in providing oral health services.', '<p>The clinic, equipped with the most modern technical means, guarantees the high quality of the provided service. Our clinic consists of 5 offices equipped with new generation dental devices, including an operating room.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;Highly qualified specialists with many years of experience in all dental fields operate in the clinic, treatment is carried out at a high level in accordance with international standards.</p><p><br></p><p>Thanks to the use of the most efficient technologies and materials of the world\'s leading manufacturers, the treatment of teeth (from caries treatment to the most complex operations) is no longer a painful procedure. At the same time, the best hypoallergenic anesthetics, sedation and general anesthesia drugs of the latest generation are used, which relieve the patient from the slightest discomfort.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;In our laboratory, which is equipped with modern technologies, our laboratory staff gives you a beautiful smile with aesthetic and cosmetic work. Our laboratory has been positively evaluated by the specialists of the German brand \"Bredent\". center, and the head of the clinic, Ramiz Jalilov, is a system consultant for the \"Bredent\" company. At the same time, all constructions made in the laboratory are made according to the protocols of the German \"Bredent\" company.</p>');

