(1, 'Telman Hacıyev Hacı', 'Orthodontist', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dentist (orthodontist)', '<p>After studying at Azerbaijan Medical University, I worked as an intern at Polyclinic No. 3. In 2008, I worked in various clinics.I am currently working as an orthodontist at the” White tooth \" clinic . This task includes : - Treatment of tooth row curvature, jaw defects with braces and functional devices ; - Orthopedic pre-work ; - Orthognotic pre-surgical preparation ; - Treatment with braces and functional means to solve the problem in the jaw joint</p>', '2024-04-02 15:06:19', '2024-04-14 11:23:58', NULL, NULL, 1, 2, 0, 1, 'telman-haciyev-haci'),
(2, 'Orxan Novruzov Canpolad', 'Doctor-dentist (therapist, endodontist)', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/dr.orxan_novruzov_?igsh=MWZzZGpjdTlxaGNscA==', '', 'Doctor-dentist (therapist, endodontist)', '<p>I, Orkhan Novruzov, graduated from Penza State University in 2016 and was admitted to residency that year. During this year, I worked in the State Polyclinic and private clinics. In 2021, I will return to Baku and work as a therapist-endodontist at the Bayaz Dental clinic.<br>This position includes:<br>- Canal treatment<br>- Caries treatment, professional hygiene;<br>- Aesthetic restoration of teeth;<br>- Professional hygiene;<br>- Treatment under sedation;<br>In the work we do, we pay attention to the first quality, and the second to the comfort of the patient.</p>', '2024-04-02 15:08:12', '2024-04-14 12:24:19', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, 0, 1, 'orxan-novruzov-canpolad'),
(3, 'Aydan Məmmədli Yalçın', 'Doctor-dentist (therapist, orthopedist, pediatric dentist)', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/dr_aydanmammadli?igsh=MWtwbzJvZmp1dGptMA==', 'https://www.instagram.com/dr_aydanmammadli?igsh=MWtwbzJvZmp1dGptMA==', 'Doctor-dentist (therapist, orthopedist, pediatric dentist)', '<p>I, Dr. Aydan Mammadli, worked as a dentist-therapist at the State Hospital for 2 years after receiving my education at Krikkale University in Turkey. After coming to Azerbaijan, I started working at Beyaz Dish dental clinic. I have been working as a dentist-therapist in the clinic for more than 1 year. This position includes: - Caries treatment; - Canal treatment; - Aesthetic restoration of teeth; - Treatment under sedation; - Professional hygiene; - Children\'s dentistry &nbsp; &nbsp; My team and I work hard to give you a beautiful smile.</p>', '2024-04-02 15:12:27', '2024-04-14 12:25:17', NULL, NULL, 5, 6, 0, 1, 'aydan-məmmədli-yalcin'),
(4, 'Nihad Abbasov Elşən', 'Doctor-dentist, prosthodontist (therapist, orthopedist, implantologist)', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/dr_abbasov_?igsh=MXVpd2h4MzE0cHM2YQ==', '', 'Doctor-dentist, prosthodontist (therapist, orthopedist, implantologist)', '<p>I, Dr. Nihad Abbasov, graduated from the Medical Stomatological Academy of Ukraine in 2015 and continued my post-graduate studies at the Department of Maxillofacial Surgery at the same university. After returning to Baku in 2018, I started working as a prosthodontist at the \"Beyaz Diş\" dental clinic. Areas included in this position:<br>- Preparation of orthopedic constructions<br>- Preparation of inlay, onlay, overlay type constructions<br>- Placement of implants<br>- Aesthetic restoration of teeth</p>', '2024-04-02 15:13:48', '2024-04-14 12:25:40', NULL, NULL, 7, 8, 0, 1, 'nihad-abbasov-elsən'),
(5, 'Nicat Abbasov Elşən', 'Doctor-dentist (surgeon, implantologist)', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/dr.nijat?igsh=MXVodzJsdGNxc3p3MQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr', '', 'Doctor-dentist (surgeon, implantologist)', '<p>Mən , doktor Nicat Abbasov 2014-ci ildə Ukrayna Medikal Stomatoloji Akademiyada təhsilimi aldıqdan sonra , 2017-ci ilə kimi həmin universitetin üst çənə cərahiyyəsi kafedrasında ardinatura təhsilimi dəvam etdirmişəm. 2018-ci ildən ehtibarən Bəyaz Diş stomatoloji klinikasında həkim-stomatoloq kimi fəaliyyət göstərirəm.<br>Fəaliyyət göstərdiyim ilk günlərdən cərrahi prosedurları klinikada həyata keçirdirəm və stomatoloq-cərrah vəzifəsində çalışıram.<br>Bu vəzifəyə daxildir:<br>- Ağıl dişlərinin çəkimi;<br>- Implant əməliyyatları;<br>- Sinus lifting və agumentasiya əməliyyatı;I, Dr. Nijat Abbasov, after receiving my education at the Ukrainian Medical Stomatological Academy in 2014, continued my postgraduate studies at the Department of Maxillofacial Surgery of that university until 2017. Since 2018, I have been working as a dentist at Beyaz Diş dental clinic.<br>Since the first days of my activity, I have been performing surgical procedures in the clinic and working as a dentist-surgeon.<br>This position includes:<br>- Weight of wisdom teeth;<br>- Implant operations;<br>- Sinus lifting and augmentation surgery;</p>', '2024-04-02 15:16:28', '2024-04-14 12:26:07', NULL, NULL, 9, 10, 0, 1, 'nicad-abbasov-elsən');

